{%- comment -%}
  About Us page (templates/page.about-us.json). Copy supplied by Chris (Jul 2026).
  The founder photo can be swapped in the theme editor; it falls back to the
  bundled HeadshotChris.jpg asset so the card never renders empty.
{%- endcomment -%}
<section class="about-page">
  <div class="container">
    <header class="about-head">
      <span class="kicker">{{ section.settings.kicker }}</span>
      <h1>{{ section.settings.heading }}</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="about-body">
      <h2>Why Ready Eddie&trade;?</h2>
      <p>We love solving everyday problems with simple ideas. Ready Eddie&trade; was created to solve a simple but surprisingly common problem:</p>
      <blockquote class="about-quote">How do you know when your trash has been picked up without walking down the driveway to check?</blockquote>
      <p>Like many homeowners, we found ourselves making unnecessary trips to the street just to see whether the garbage truck had already come. We wanted a simple, reliable solution that didn&rsquo;t require batteries, Wi-Fi, apps, or an engineering degree.</p>
      <p>That idea became Ready Eddie&trade; &mdash; an easy-to-install visual indicator that lets you know when your trash or recycling bin has been emptied.</p>

      <h2>Designed for Real Life</h2>
      <p>Ready Eddie&trade; is especially helpful for:</p>
      <ul class="about-list">
        <li>Homeowners with long driveways</li>
        <li>Seniors who want fewer unnecessary trips outside</li>
        <li>Busy families</li>
        <li>Anyone who might enjoy knowing when their trash or recycling bin has been emptied &mdash; sometimes the simplest ideas make everyday life just a little easier.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Built to Last</h2>
      <p>Ready Eddie&trade; is designed to withstand outdoor conditions and provide years of dependable use with no batteries, electronics, or maintenance required.</p>
      <p>Our goal is to create practical products that solve everyday problems through simple, thoughtful design.</p>

      <h2>About Ready Eddie&trade; Shop</h2>
      <p>Bin Ready, LLC is the company behind the Ready Eddie&trade; brand and operates ReadyEddieShop.com.</p>
      <p>We are a U.S.-based, family-owned small business focused on designing practical products that improve everyday life.</p>
      <p>Ready Eddie&trade; products are manufactured in the U.S. to ensure consistent quality and durability.</p>

      <h2>Our Commitment</h2>
      <p>We appreciate every customer who chooses to support our small, family-owned business, and we are committed to providing:</p>
      <ul class="about-list">
        <li>Quality products</li>
        <li>Fast, friendly customer service</li>
        <li>Secure online ordering</li>
        <li>Fast, free shipping within the United States</li>
        <li>A satisfaction guarantee</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Thank you for visiting Ready Eddie Shop and supporting our mission.</p>

      <aside class="about-founder">
        {%- if section.settings.founder_photo -%}
          <img
            class="about-founder-photo"
            src="{{ section.settings.founder_photo | image_url: width: 480 }}"
            alt="Chris, the inventor of Ready Eddie"
            width="{{ section.settings.founder_photo.width }}"
            height="{{ section.settings.founder_photo.height }}"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        {%- else -%}
          <img
            class="about-founder-photo"
            src="{{ 'HeadshotChris.jpg' | asset_url }}"
            alt="Chris, the inventor of Ready Eddie"
            width="472"
            height="1024"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        {%- endif -%}
        <div class="about-founder-text">
          <p>{{ section.settings.founder_note }}</p>
          <p class="about-founder-sig">&mdash;&nbsp;&nbsp;<strong>{{ settings.founder_name | default: 'Chris Krebs' }}</strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;{{ settings.founder_role | default: 'Maker, Ready Eddie' }}</p>
        </div>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "About us",
  "settings": [
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "kicker",
      "label": "Kicker (small text above heading)",
      "default": "A family-owned U.S. small business"
    },
    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "heading",
      "label": "Page heading",
      "default": "About Us"
    },
    {
      "type": "image_picker",
      "id": "founder_photo",
      "label": "Founder photo",
      "info": "Defaults to the bundled headshot if left empty."
    },
    {
      "type": "textarea",
      "id": "founder_note",
      "label": "Founder note (next to the photo)",
      "default": "Hi, I'm Chris, the inventor of Ready Eddie™. Thanks for visiting our store and supporting a U.S. small business."
    }
  ],
  "presets": [
    {
      "name": "About us"
    }
  ]
}
{% endschema %}
